/// Test workflow that sleeps for a configurable duration (BT-1498).
///
/// Takes a sleep duration (ms) as input and sleeps for that long.
/// Used to test WorkflowHandle timeout behavior.
///
///   engine startWorkflow: SlowWorkflow id: "wf-1" args: #(5000)
Workflow subclass: SlowWorkflow

  /// Sleep for the given duration (ms) and return #done.
  class run: durationMs ctx: ctx =>
    ctx sleep: durationMs
    #done
